config file to load instead of $HOME/.torsmorc
.TP
\fB\-d\fR
daemonize, fork to background
.TP
\fB\-f\fR FONT
font to use
.TP
\fB\-h\fR
help
.TP
\fB\-o\fR
create own window to draw
.TP
\fB\-b\fR
double buffer (prevents flickering)
.TP
